---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="주문 완료 | Family Coffee Bar" description="주문이 접수되었습니다.">
  <section class="sticker-card text-center">
    <p class="sticker-chip inline-flex">Order Received</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold text-roast">주문이 접수되었습니다</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink/85">곧 한 잔씩 내려서 전달해 드릴게요. 원두 페이지로 돌아가 다른 설명도 읽어보세요.</p>

    <div class="mt-6 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <a
        href="/beans"
        class="touch-target inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-roast px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-paper"
      >
        원두 다시 보기
      </a>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="touch-target inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-roast/30 bg-paper px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-roast"
      >
        홈으로 이동
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
